item.title: SoftLayer_Network_Firewall_AccessControlList
item.description: SoftLayer_Network_Firewall_AccessControlList Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Network_Firewall_AccessControlList data type contains general information relating to a single SoftLayer firewall access to controll list. This is the object which ties the running rules to a specific context. Use the [[SoftLayer Network Firewall Template]] service to pull SoftLayer recommended rule set templates. Use the [[SoftLayer Network Firewall Update Request]] service to submit a firewall update request. Local direction Type: string
